        "CHAOS__SPEC": "Inquinatus Globus Igneus",
        "CHAOS__SPEC_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsDamage>Incendere</style>. Globo igneo custodi pro usque ad <style=cIsUtility>10s</style>, qui <style=cIsDamage>400%-2000% damni</style> infligit et terram urit <style=cIsDamage>10%</style> damni per secundam inferens. Custodiens per <style=cIsUtility>5s</style> minimum Chaos radium mortis loco emittere facit, <style=cIsDamage>2000% damni</style> per secundam inferens. Custodiens ultra <style=cIsUtility>5s</style> durationem radii mortis auget.",
